  "description": "A picturesque coastal scene at sunrise or sunset. The sun is low on the horizon, partially obscured by distant landmasses, creating a bright golden glow that reflects on the rippling surface of the water. Waves are breaking near the shore, with white foam visible against the dark blue of the sea. The foreground is a beach composed of dark, grainy sand. A lone wooden post is visible, partially buried in the sand. The sky transitions from a vibrant orange near the horizon to a soft blue above.",
